import React from 'react';
import { Paper, Typography, Box } from '@mui/material';

function Help() {
  return (
    <Paper elevation={3} sx={{ p: 3 }}>
      <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
        Help & Support
      </Typography>
      <Box sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
        <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
          How to use the app:
        </Typography>
        <Typography paragraph>
          1. Add tasks using the input field in the Tasks section
        </Typography>
        <Typography paragraph>
          2. Mark tasks as complete by clicking the checkbox
        </Typography>
        <Typography paragraph>
          3. Delete tasks using the delete icon
        </Typography>
        <Typography paragraph>
          4. View deleted tasks in the Recently Deleted section
        </Typography>
      </Box>
    </Paper>
  );
}

export default Help;
